<template lang='pug'>
    .about
        block-header
        poster
        screenlife
        team
        form-questions
        block-footer
</template>

<script>
    import Header from '../blocks/includes/header.vue';
    import Footer from '../blocks/includes/footer.vue';

    import Poster from '../blocks/about/poster.vue';
    import Screenlife from '../blocks/about/screenlife.vue';
    import Team from '../blocks/about/team.vue';
    import Form from '../blocks/about/form.vue';
    import AOS from 'aos';

    export default {
        name: 'About',
        function(){
            return {}
        },
        components:{
			'block-header': Header,
            'block-footer': Footer,
            'poster': Poster,
            'screenlife': Screenlife,
            'team': Team,
            'form-questions': Form
        },
        mounted() {
			this.$nextTick(function() {
				AOS.init({
					once: true,
					disabled: 'mobile',
					// offset: 0,
					duration: 1000
				});
			});
		}
    }
</script>

<style lang="scss">
	@import '@/assets/sass/ui.scss';
	@import '@/helpers/sass/aos.scss';
</style>
